{"type": "article", "id": 16045, "title": "智能水杯", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-14T07:08:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125738FXzfeNrscCWyIVZ6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款智能水杯能与手机上的专用 APP 连接，相当于一个喝水管家。在上面输入身高体重以计算每日的饮水量，就可以检测你的饮水情况了，必要的时候能提醒你记得喝水而不是等口渴时才喝。它同时能感应咖啡，提醒咖啡因的吸取量。智能水杯由美国 San Jose 的 Groking lab 开发 ，有灰、紫、蓝、红四种颜色可选，现在正在众筹，<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/ozmo/ozmo-smart-cup-water-hydration-and-coffee-enjoymen/description\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。 </a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614343165uZdBGfRXNczUFe.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"382\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50933333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143432lyLYJvtwOXrdzKfI.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143433DI5K2Oed6QLmw3rn.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143434SNwRb87Ttl9gMJ5V.gif\" width=\"680\" height=\"463\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68088235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143436khp0ADSwlRxCHbz6.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}